short_summary: Procurement Notice for the supply of 67 GHz Analyzer (Request for Proposal)
description:
The department of Innovation, Science and Economic Development Canada has a requirement for the items listed below or equivalent category.


1. 1331.6751.02 Extension to 8 GB IQ memory FSW-B108
2.  1331.1545.02 EUTRA/LTE FDD Downlink measurement application FSW-K100
3. 1331.1551.02 EUTRA/LTE FDD Uplink measurement application FSW-K101
4. 1338.3606.02 5G NR R15 downlink measurement application FSW-K144
5. 1338.3612.02 5G NR R15 uplink measurement application FSW-K145
6. 1338.6486.02 3GPP 5G-NR Combined ACLR/SEM and EVM FSW-K147
7. 1350.6624.02 5G NR R16 Extension for UL/DL FSW-K148
8. 1350.7108.02 5G NR R17 DL/UL measurement application FSW-K171
9. 1313.1400.02 EMI measurement application for diagnostic of RF interference FSW-K54
10.  331.5932.02 CISPR calibration for FSW-K54 FSW-K54CAL
11.  1337.7495.02 Transient measurement application FSW-K601
12.  1322.9745.02 Transient measurements, chirp analysis FSW-K60C
